fundraiserunsubscribe-query: Ask if the user wants to remove email address:$1 from the fundraising mail lists. Leave email as is; a different templating engine is being used.
fundraiserunsubscribe-info:
Unused at this time.

Information on how the unsubscribe request will be processed.

Parameters:
* $1 - email address
fundraiserunsubscribe-submit:
Label for button which will unsubscribe them from the fundraising email list.
{{Identical|Unsubscribe}}
fundraiserunsubscribe-cancel:
Label for button which will cancel the unsubscribe process and redirect them to the WMF homepage.
{{Identical|Cancel}}
fundraiserunsubscribe-errormsg:
Text to display if the unsubscribe failed. Link to email address:$1 for more support.

Parameters:
* $1 - email address
fundraiserunsubscribe-success: Message indicating that everything that can be done to unsubscribe them has been done.
fundraiserunsubscribe-sucesswarning: Notification to the user that there might be some manual operations or ongoing things that will take time to clear. Will always be shown with fundraiserunsubscribe-success. $1 is an email address for them to contact if they have further questions.
fundraisersubscribe: Title shown on page letting users opt in to emails.
fundraisersubscribe-fail:
Text to display if the opt-in failed. Link to email address:$1 for more support.

Parameters:
* $1 - email address
fundraisersubscribe-success:
Message to tell the user the opt-in submission was successful.
{{Identical|Thank you}}
fundraisersubscribe-opt-in-continue-001: Text for the opt-in button variant 001
fundraisersubscribe-page-title-001: Title of the opt-in page variant 001
fundraisersubscribe-page-subtitle-001: Subtitle of the opt-in page variant 001
fundraisersubscribe-appeal-headline-001: Appeal headline for opt-in page variant 001
fundraisersubscribe-appeal-text-001: Appeal text for opt-in page variant 001
fundraisersubscribe-privacy-text-001:
Text informing the donor how their email address will be used, with a link to our privacy policy, variation 001.
* $1 - link to privacy policy
fundraisersubscribe-photo-credit:
Template for giving credit to a photo author in the wle_001 opt-in variant
